<p style="Normal" xid="114" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Можно сразу создать столбцы в таблице командой <c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">rails g model  Article title:string text:text</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="93" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Articl</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">e название модели, </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">title:string</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> столбец  ---  title - название столбца,  string  ее свойства. Этой командой мы создаем сразу миграцию с готовой заполненной таблицей модель article.rb и юнит тесты-  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">test/models/article_test.rb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">  и </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">test/fixtures/articles.yml</c></p>
